data.description: This versatile and spacious two-story Trenton plan gives an inviting ambiance to guests with more than 2,300+ sqft of living space to enjoy. This plan features not only a first floor flex room, but also an upstairs bonus room for homeowners looking to make this space their own. Other notable features of the Trenton include designer finishes throughout the home, a covered patio space, 2-car garage, corner pantry, and kitchen island . The addition of upstairs powder bath and closet is ideal for visiting guests – or kids looking for a space to call their own.
